<i>adverb</i>: 과감히 [과ː감히], 감히 [감ː히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>과감히 [과ː감히]</dt><br>
<dd>boldly</dd><br>
<dd>결단력이 있고 용감하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Decisively and bravely.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>감히 [감ː히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. daringly; boldly</dd><br>
<dd>두렵거나 어렵지만 그래도.</dd><br>
<dd>Although one feels scared or uncomfortable.</dd><br>
<dd>2. impudently</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동이 주제넘게.</dd><br>
<dd>Presumptiously in speaking or behaving.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>